struct vsip::impl::Reduce_is_expr_dense
File: ../../../vsip/opt/expr/eval_dense.hpp

Expression reduction to determine if an expression consists of dense data at the leaves (either blocks with stride_unit_dense packing, subviews that are dense, or scalar_blocks). Check is done at runtime, checking for gaps in highest-dimension stride.
